race.description: Bet With Betdeluxe App 5Th Grade F
race.comment: ART OF DECEPTION (5) goes very well here starting 14 times for five wins and five minors. Placed last time (19.60) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten 2 lengths. Appeals as a leading chance in this. HARA'S SQUASH (2) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (19.79) at this track in a Grade 5. Lines up from box 2 for the first time. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Can measure up. MORE THAN MERRY (1) has found the minor placings here at last couple of runs, finishing third last time beaten 1.3 lengths (19.74). Has a win and eight places times at this track. Expected to be in this for a long way. HARA'S PUMPKIN (6) racing over this distance brings the best out in her. Something for the Multiples: KYOTO (4)
